Adds a record to request log.

Parameters:
requestName - request name
documentId - document ID of the document associated with the request
requestDate - request invocation date
remoteApplicationShortName - name of the remote application that sent the request
userCode - code of the user who sent the request
organizationCode - the organization that sent the request
additionalInformation - additional information
Returns:
